title: Sinn Féin in government will deliver better healthcare, housing and childcare - Adams (Sinn Féin) ...
text: ( Source : Sinn Féin ) 10 October , 2015 - by Gerry Adams TD Sinn Féin Leader Gerry Adams TD highlighted the inequality at the heart of Fine Gael / Labour policy , and outlined Sinn Féin's policy plans for better healthcare, housing and childcare.
